reviewText: This was the second disaster of a movie which came together with "Lo que callamos las mujeres" Both very boring I would like to return both movies.
It had all of the hits that my grandmother loves, I was very please with it and so was my grandmother!
THESE SERIES ARE OF THE MIRACLES OUR LADY ~~ THE MOTHER OF OUR LORD ~~ HAS GRANTED ALL WHO SEEK HER HELP.  I WATCH THEM ON TV BUT WAS GLAD I WAS ABLE TO PURCHASE THEM TO OWN ~ THANKS TO AMAZON.
